  "local_port": 35102,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are the best colleges for an MBA in the world other than IIM's?",
  "response": "When considering the best colleges for an MBA program globally, several institutions are frequently highlighted for their academic rigor, global reputation, and network opportunities. Here are some of the top MBA programs other than the Indian Institutes of Management (IIMs):\n\n1. **Harvard Business School (HBS)** - USA\n   - Known for its case study method and strong alumni network.\n\n2. **Stanford Graduate School of Business** - USA\n   - Offers a collaborative environment with close ties to Silicon Valley.\n\n3. **The Wharton School, University of Pennsylvania** - USA\n   - Renowned for its finance program and leadership development.\n\n4. **London Business School (LBS)** - UK\n   - Offers a diverse, global perspective with proximity to the financial hub of London.\n\n5. **INSEAD** - France/Singapore/Abu Dhabi\n   - Known for its international focus and campuses across the globe.\n\n6. **MIT Sloan School of Management** - USA\n   - Emphasizes innovation and entrepreneurship.\n\n7. **Chicago Booth School of Business, University of Chicago** - USA\n   - Offers a flexible curriculum with an analytical approach.\n\n8. **Columbia Business School, Columbia University** - USA\n   - Located in New York City, offering extensive business connections.\n\n9. **IESE Business School, University of Navarra** - Spain\n   - Focuses on ethical leadership and global business.\n\n10. **HEC Paris** - France\n    - Offers robust alumni connections and strong European ties.\n\n11. **Kellogg School of Management, Northwestern University** - USA\n    - Known for marketing and management programs.\n\n12. **Haas School of Business, University of California, Berkeley** - USA\n    - Strong emphasis on social responsibility and sustainability.\n\n13. **Said Business School, University of Oxford** - UK\n    - Known for combining business with traditional academic strengths.\n\n14. **Judge Business School, University of Cambridge** - UK\n    - Offers a one-year intensive program with access to Cambridge's resources.\n\n15. **IMD Business School** - Switzerland\n    - Offers intensive leadership development and personal growth.\n\nThese schools are renowned for their rigorous academic environments, extensive alumni networks, and unique specializations. It's important to consider factors like program fit, culture, location, and long-term career goals when selecting an MBA program.",
